---
import { config } from "../../../data/config";

---

<section class="bg-black overflow-hidden relative border-b border-border-soft">
  <div class="motion-drift absolute inset-y-10 left-0 hidden w-64 rounded-r-full bg-gold/12 blur-3xl lg:block"></div>
  <div class="motion-drift absolute right-0 top-12 hidden h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-wine/10 blur-3xl lg:block" style="--float-delay: 1.1s"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 lg:py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:items-center lg:gap-16">
      <div data-reveal="blur" class="relative flex flex-col gap-5">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gold">
          <span class="h-px w-10 bg-gold"></span>
          Why choose Duartes
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-text-primary font-bold leading-tight text-h1">
          Premium care without the dealership wait.
        </h2>
        <p
          data-reveal="up"
          style="--reveal-delay: 120ms"
          class="max-w-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed"
        >
          Mobile detailing should feel effortless. We arrive with the right tools, the right products, and the discipline to leave every surface cleaner, richer, and better protected than when we arrived.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div
          data-reveal="blur"
          style="--reveal-delay: 160ms"
          class="motion-card-hover relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-wine/18 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(110,43,44,0.14),rgba(23,24,27,0.96))] p-6 shadow-lg"
        >
          <div class="motion-sheen"></div>
          <div class="motion-glow-pulse absolute -right-8 -top-8 h-24 w-24 rounded-full bg-wine/14 blur-2xl"></div>
          <p class="text-gold font-semibold text-lg italic">
            "It's not just a cleaning - it's a transformation."
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            At Duartes Auto Detailing, we believe true detailing is about carefully restoring the condition, presentation, and protection of every vehicle we touch. We bring professional mobile service, quality products, and obsessive attention to detail directly to your home or office.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <div
            data-reveal="scale"
            style="--reveal-delay: 220ms"
            class="motion-card-hover relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border-soft bg-surface-2 px-5 py-5 text-center"
          >
            <div class="absolute inset-x-5 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-wine-soft/75 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="motion-glow-pulse absolute -right-6 -top-6 h-20 w-20 rounded-full bg-gold/8 blur-2xl"></div>
            <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl" data-count-to={config.vehiclesDetailed} data-count-suffix="+" data-count-duration="1800">{config.vehiclesDetailed}+</span>
            <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-text-secondary">Vehicles Detailed</span>
          </div>
          <div
            data-reveal="scale"
            style="--reveal-delay: 320ms"
            class="motion-card-hover relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border-soft bg-surface-2 px-5 py-5 text-center"
          >
            <div class="absolute inset-x-5 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-gold/70 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="motion-glow-pulse absolute -right-6 -top-6 h-20 w-20 rounded-full bg-gold/8 blur-2xl" style="--float-delay: 0.8s"></div>
            <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl" data-count-to={config.yearsOfExperience} data-count-suffix="+" data-count-duration="1100">{config.yearsOfExperience}+</span>
            <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-text-secondary">Years of Experience</span>
          </div>
          <div
            data-reveal="scale"
            style="--reveal-delay: 420ms"
            class="motion-card-hover relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border-soft bg-surface-2 px-5 py-5 text-center"
          >
            <div class="absolute inset-x-5 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-wine-soft/75 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="motion-glow-pulse absolute -right-6 -top-6 h-20 w-20 rounded-full bg-wine/12 blur-2xl" style="--float-delay: 1.2s"></div>
            <span class="text-gold font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl" data-count-to={config.bayAreaLocations} data-count-suffix="+" data-count-duration="1600">{config.bayAreaLocations}+</span>
            <span class="mt-2 block text-sm text-text-secondary">Locations Served</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
